000012B6                           551  ; BTNSELCL IF THE MOUSE IS INSIDE BUT THE MOUSE BUTTON IS NOT PRESSED AND
000012B6                           552  ; BTNPRSCL IF THE MOUSE BUTTON IS PRESSED INSIDE.
000012B6                           553  ; INPUT    : A0 - POINTER TO THE VARIABLE DATABLOCK
000012B6                           554  ; OUTPUT   : NONE
