00001854                          1344  ; -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
00001854                          1345  GOLINIT
00001854                          1346  ; INITIALIZE GAME OF LIFE APPLICATION AS FOLLOWS:
00001854                          1347  ; * MAKES THE INTERNAL STATE TO BE "PAUSED/STOPPED"
00001854                          1348  ; * INITIALIZES THE USER INTERFACE (BY INITIALIZING THE BUTTONS LIST AND
00001854                          1349  ;   ADDING BUTTONS INTO IT)
00001854                          1350  ; * INITIALIZES THE GRID.
00001854                          1351  ; * INITIALIZES THE UTILITY CODE.
00001854                          1352  ; INPUT    : NONE
00001854                          1353  ; OUTPUT   : NONE
00001854                          1354  ; MODIFIES : NONE
00001854                          1355  ; -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
