000018AE                          1374  ; UPDATE GAME OF LIFE APPLICATION AS FOLLOWS:
000018AE                          1375  ; * UPDATES THE BUTTON LIST
000018AE                          1376  ; * EXECUTES CODE DEPENDING ON THE CURRENT APPLICATION STATE.
